INSERT INTO `users` (`vFirstName`, `vLastName`, `vUserName`, `vEmail`, `vMobileNo`, `vProfileImage`, `dDob`, `tAddress`, `vCity`, `dLatitude`, `dLongitude`, `vStateName`, `vZipCode`, `vGender`, `iAge`, `eStatus`, `dtAddedAt`, `dtUpdatedAt`, `eDeviceType`, `vDeviceModel`, `vDeviceOS`, `vDeviceToken`, `vEmailVerificationCode`, `vAccessToken`, `eSocialLoginType`, `vSocialLoginId`, `eEmailVerified`, `vTermsConditionsVersion`, `vPrivacyPolicyVersion`) VALUES ('Gayatri', 'Patole', '', 'gtshbwiida@privaterelay.appleid.com', '', '978307200_5fb52ce17b2c3.png', '1997-12-07', '', 'Texas City', '29.383845', '-94.9027002', 'Texas', '', '', '22', 'Active', NOW(), '', 'iOS', 'iPhone 7 Plus', '13.2.3', '93D30DE6E85C6A0B8674FB4C53C4C03238C69F362D70882C4E3D1986FE0EEACD', '', 'd546822d5932ab5b7cbcd9b8c967aa9b1c17172395ffe37bead5c12537fdb652', 'apple', '001115.43868751454d4703a431931c804e1943.1358', 'Yes', '3.0', '6.0')

SELECT `u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vUserName` AS `u_user_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `u_profile_image`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `u_city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `u_state`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`eEmailVerified` AS `u_email_verified`,`u`.`vAccessToken` AS `u_access_token`,`u`.`eDeviceType` AS `u_device_type`,`u`.`vDeviceModel` AS `u_device_model`,`u`.`vDeviceOS` AS `u_device_os`,`u`.`vDeviceToken` AS `u_device_token`,`u`.`dtAddedAt` AS `u_added_at`,`u`.`eSocialLoginType` AS `u_social_login_type`,`u`.`vSocialLoginId` AS `u_social_login_id`,`u`.`eOneTimeTransaction` AS `e_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`tOneTimeTransaction` AS `t_one_time_transaction`,`u`.`ePushNotify` AS `u_push_notify`,`u`.`vTermsConditionsVersion` AS `terms_conditions_version`,`u`.`vPrivacyPolicyVersion` AS `privacy_policy_version`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS email_user_name,`u`.`eLogStatus` AS `u_log_status_updated`,`u`.`eIsSubscribed` AS `u_is_subscribed`,`u`.`tReceiptData` AS `u_receipt_data`,`u`.`vSubscriptionId` AS `u_subscription_id`,`u`.`vGender` AS `u_gender` FROM `users` AS `u` WHERE `u`.`iUserId` = 16  LIMIT 1
